System Requirements\

\fs22 \ulnone \
LaTeXiT 1.14.4 requires Mac OS X version 10.3.9 (Panther version) or 10.4 or above (Tiger version), and a working LaTeX installation with at least pdflatex and GhostScript (gs). If you do not know what these programs are, you can look at the "Install LaTeX" section of this document.\

\f2\b\fs26 \

\f1\b0 \ul Install/Uninstall\

\fs22 \ulnone \
Install : Simply drag and drop LaTeXiT from the image disk into your "Applications" folder, or any other place you want on your hard-drive.\
Uninstall : LaTeXiT creates a folder in Library/Application Support/LaTeXiT of your home folder. If you plan to uninstall LaTeXiT (by dropping its icon in the trash), you might also want to remove this folder.
\f2\b\fs26 \
