\cf0 LaTeX Palettes\

\fs22 \ulnone \
Since version 1.14.4, LaTeXiT handles LaTeX palettes as plugins. Built-in palettes are inside the application, but additional palettes can be installed inside the Library folders, in a sub-folder Application Support/LaTeXiT/Palettes.\
Examples :\
/Library/Application Support/LaTeXiT/Palettes\
/Users/[your name]/Library/Application Support/LaTeXiT/Palettes\
/Network/Library/Application Support/LaTeXiT/Palettes\
\
A palette is a folder with the following structure:\
name.latexpalette\
     |_Info.plist\
     |_Resources\
          |_English.lproj
\fs26 \ul \

\fs22 \ulnone                |_Localizable.strings\
          |_French.lproj\
               |_Localizable.strings\
          |...image files...\
\
